OL,3,CProtection demanded for 'toilet bowl'
OL,4,Charbour water in Christchurch
OL,6,FLast year there were more than four
OL,7,Fhundred releases of raw sewage
OL,8,Faffecting Christchurch mainly from the
OL,9,Ffour Wessex Water treatment works
OL,10,Fupstream from Christchurch.
OL,12,FCharles Watson from River Action said:
OL,13,F"It is not an exaggeration to state
OL,14,Fthat Christchurch Harbour has become
OL,15,Fthe toilet bowl of Bournemouth because
OL,16,Fcoming down the River Stour enormous
OL,17,Fvolumes of untreated sewage are being
OL,18,Fspilt and dumped by wastewater
OL,19,Ftreatment plants."
