OL,6,FIn a statement, Wessex Water told ITV
OL,7,FNews Meridian: "Storm overflows
OL,8,Foperate to protect properties from
OL,9,Fflooding and discharge mostly
OL,10,Frainwater or groundwater, but we agree
OL,11,Fthey are outdated and we're spending
OL,12,F#3 million every month on schemes to
OL,13,Freduce how often this happens in our
OL,14,Fregion.
OL,16,F"This investment will more than double
OL,17,Ffrom next year, if approved by Ofwat."
